Test Name: Rabbit Urine Proteins and Serum IgE/Protein Analysis
Purpose: To accurately quantify proteins in rabbit urine and measure IgE and other protein concentrations in rabbit serum.
Container: Sterile urine container for urine; red-top or serum separator tube for serum
Equipment: Urinalysis analyzer, ELISA kit with microplate reader, protein assay kit with spectrophotometer, centrifuge, micropipettes
